Notice:

1. "simple set" and "Standard" are only different from accessories set, "simple set" is NO headset and original box, it is easier for customs clearance in some countries.

2. Both "simple set" and "Standard" phones are with FACE ID.

About Bundle:

"simple set" means you will get iPhone11 cellphone with Wall charger + Data cable(No original box, No earphone);

"Standard" means you will get iPhone 11 cell phone with Standard package;

"add wireless charger" means you will get iPhone 11 mobile phone with Standard package+wireless charger.

Standard Package including:

1* iPhone 11 original unlocked Cellphone

1* charger(US/EU/UK/AU plugs optional)

1* manual book

1* earphone

1* data cable

Free Gifts:

1 x Silicon case

1 x Screen protetor

Original Unlocked Apple iPhone 11 RAM 4GB ROM 64GB/128GB/256GB Mobile Phone LTE 6.1" Hexa Core IOS Fingerprint Face ID NFC in Sealed box
